’Щ@accdb87dc3bb9f8af99c5aeb77952b3985aa22c135d30467c0a01cd27bd9b4bdЩұTitle: title: polars into-nu
Path: Flags
Content:
``--rows, -n {number}``
: Number of rows to be shown.
``--tail, -t``
: Shows tail rows.
``--index, -i``
: Add an index column.
